abstract: A history of resistance underlies Zuccotti Park, where the Chock Full o' Nuts chain held out 13 years and delayed the completion of the privately built park.
snippet: A history of resistance underlies Zuccotti Park, where the Chock Full o' Nuts chain held out 13 years and delayed the completion of the privately built park.
lead_paragraph: Resistance runs deep at Zuccotti Park. You might even say it's in the ground. The protesters clinging tenaciously to that little parcel in Lower Manhattan owe a big spiritual debt to Chock Full o' Nuts.

headline.main: Holding Out at Zuccotti Park Is a 44-Year-Old Tradition
